##  Repository Structure

The repository is organized as follows:

```text
├── Code/
│   └── analysis_script.Rmd       # R Markdown source code for all plots
├── Data/
│   └── 2000-2021_Turkey_Fire.csv # Processed NASA FIRMS dataset
├── Plots/
│   ├── Map.png                   # High-res spatial map
│   ├── Monthly.png               # Seasonal analysis chart
│   ├── Yearly.png                # Annual trend line chart
│   ├── Lollipop.png              # Causes of fires chart
│   └── Afforestation.png         # Rehabilitation area chart
├── Poster.pdf                    # Final A1 Project Poster
└── README.md                     # Project documentation (this file)

```

---

## Data Sources

1. **NASA FIRMS (Satellite Data):**
* *Dataset:* Fire Information for Resource Management System (FIRMS) [2000-2021].
* *Access:* Retrieved via Kaggle (NASA Earthdata).
* *Usage:* Spatial mapping, seasonal, and annual analysis.


2. **General Directorate of Forestry (OGM):**
* *Source:* Republic of Türkiye General Directorate of Forestry.
* *Document:* [2024 Administrative Activity Report (Faaliyet Raporu)](https://www.ogm.gov.tr/tr/faaliyet-raporu)
* *Note:* The original PDF file exceeds 100MB, so it is accessed via the official external link above.
* *Usage:* Analysis of fire causes and rehabilitation efforts (Table 22).



